suggestions.original: To improve the color contrast in the artwork, consider using darker outlines or shadows around the characters and elements to make them stand out more against the background. Additionally, increasing the saturation of the colors used for the dragons and the characters' clothing can help them pop more. Using complementary colors for the background and the main elements can also enhance the overall visual impact.
